account.descriptionLink:
This proposal concerns the permanent closure of bridge-based migrations from Arbitrum to STKAI on Solana.

It is proposed that all tokens that are either unclaimed or do not have a support ticket raised by the 30th of May - be burnt and removed from supply.

If this proposal passes, StackOS and StackAI projects (and tokens) will live independently.

Please read the complete proposal on: https://medium.com/stackai-xyz/dao-proposal-last-call-for-stackos-to-stackai-migration-4bc33056c0f4
account.name: Close StackOS to StackAI migration
